{
  "id": "the-debt-collector",
  "title": "The Debt Collector",
  "description": "Whichever recruit triggers it: an old debt from before this crew catches up with them. Generic/archetypal -- not tied to a specific recruit.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "type": "start",
      "text": "A flag has been raised: one crew member's history is about to catch up with them. Origin unconfirmed.",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-notice",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "A collection notice arrives, addressed by an old alias. The manifest confirms it reached the right ship.",
      "effects": [],
      "position": {
        "x": 300,
        "y": -150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-gossip",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "After the next completed job, dockside talk turns to a name from someone's past that doesn't match the one on their contract.",
      "effects": [],
      "position": {
        "x": 300,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-flyer",
      "type": "seed",
      "seeds": [
        {
          "target": "shop",
          "params": {
            "itemName": "Faded Bounty Flyer"
          },
          "note": "A bounty flyer bearing the recruit's old alias, sold openly in port."
        }
      ],
      "completionText": "The flyer is bought up before anyone else can read it.",
      "position": {
        "x": 300,
        "y": 150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-1",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "Whatever the source, the message is the same: a debt from before this crew is still owed, and someone intends to collect.",
      "position": {
        "x": 600,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-credits",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Settle the Debt in Credits",
        "description": "Meet the creditor's agent {distance} to hand over payment before the terms get worse.",
        "difficulty": "ROUTINE",
        "tags": [
          "negotiation"
        ]
      },
      "completionText": "Payment delivered, receipt in hand.",
      "position": {
        "x": 900,
        "y": -150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-item",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Deliver the Payment in Kind",
        "description": "The creditor wants a specific item, not credits. Track it down and deliver it near {planetName}.",
        "difficulty": "STANDARD",
        "tags": [
          "recovery"
        ]
      },
      "completionText": "The item changes hands.",
      "position": {
        "x": 900,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-favor",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Work Off the Debt",
        "description": "The creditor has a job that needs doing quietly. Complete it and the debt is called even, at least for now."
      },
      "completionText": "The favor is done.",
      "position": {
        "x": 900,
        "y": 150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-2",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The creditor confirms receipt -- and, in the same breath, raises the stakes for what happens if this ever happens again.",
      "position": {
        "x": 1200,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-choice",
      "type": "choice",
      "text": "How does the crew handle the creditor going forward?",
      "choiceOptions": [
        {
          "id": "confront",
          "label": "Confront the creditor directly"
        },
        {
          "id": "rally",
          "label": "Have the crew cover the rest of the debt together"
        },
        {
          "id": "cutrun",
          "label": "Let the recruit go before this happens again"
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 1500,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-confront-mission",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Corner the Creditor",
        "description": "Track the creditor down {distance} and make it clear this is the last collection they'll ever make from this crew.",
        "difficulty": "HARD",
        "tags": [
          "combat"
        ]
      },
      "completionText": "The confrontation is over.",
      "position": {
        "x": 1800,
        "y": -150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-confront-success-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The creditor backs off for good.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_perk",
          "params": {
            "perkName": "Settled Accounts"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": -300
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-confront-success-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "success",
      "text": "Whatever debt existed is settled the hard way. No one comes collecting again.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": -225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-confront-failure-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The recruit takes the worst of it.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_flaw",
          "params": {
            "flawName": "Marked"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "adjust_stat",
          "params": {
            "attribute": "will",
            "amount": -1
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": -150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-confront-failure-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "failure",
      "text": "The confrontation goes badly. The debt is gone, but so is the recruit's nerve.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": -75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-rally-attempt",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The crew pools what they can spare, hoping there are enough hands aboard to make it count.",
      "effects": [],
      "position": {
        "x": 1800,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-rally-success-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "Between the whole crew, the rest comes together fast.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_perk",
          "params": {
            "perkName": "Owed One"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-rally-success-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "success",
      "text": "The crew covers the rest between them. The debt closes clean, and everyone aboard knows it.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": 75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-rally-short-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "It isn't enough. The recruit is left to make up the difference alone, on their own time.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "adjust_stat",
          "params": {
            "attribute": "will",
            "amount": -1
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": 150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-rally-short-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "neutral",
      "text": "The crew comes up short. The debt lingers, smaller now, but still the recruit's to carry.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": 225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-cutrun-story",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "Rather than risk this again, the crew calls a vote: better to part ways clean than get pulled under by someone else's past.",
      "effects": [],
      "position": {
        "x": 1800,
        "y": 150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-cutrun-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "neutral",
      "text": "One fewer set of hands aboard, but the debt -- and whoever comes asking about it next -- is no longer this crew's problem.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": 300
      }
    }
  ],
